description:
&lt;p&gt;You will be a calm, relaxed and experienced GP receptionist who is looking to move to a friendly and supportive GP team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Experience of working in a GP surgery &amp; knowledge of EMIS Web clinical system is essential. Please apply for this role if you possess courteous, conscientious and good communication skills with the ability to work well in a team and have an enthusiastic attitude to personal development and training.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will be working on the practice reception and assisting with administrative duties. Full time and Part time contracts available, providing morning or evening shifts. Exact shifts to be agreed with suitable candidates.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will benefit from weekly 1:1 mentoring sessions with a focus upon your personal development and achieving your goals. You and your team will also benefit from quarterly team events, weekly recognition awards.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To find out more and put yourself forward apply now.&lt;/p&gt;
